reviewText:
Pros:    Good car physics,
Realistic CAR textures;
Great amount of cars;
Good tracks to start with;
Good car setup;
Multiplayer and Lan features;
The steering is great if you are a beginner because it helps you with counter steer;
A̶l̶m̶o̶s̶t̶ full wheel and pedals compatibility;
Cons:    S̶o̶u̶n̶d̶ ̶e̶r̶r̶o̶r̶s̶ ̶w̶h̶e̶n̶ ̶p̶l̶a̶y̶i̶n̶g̶ ̶i̶n̶ ̶m̶u̶l̶t̶i̶p̶l̶a̶y̶e̶r̶ (Fixed);
L̶a̶g̶ ̶o̶n̶ ̶m̶u̶l̶t̶i̶p̶l̶a̶y̶e̶r̶(Almost fixed);
L̶a̶c̶k̶ ̶o̶f̶ ̶d̶e̶t̶a̶i̶l̶s̶ ̶i̶n̶ ̶t̶h̶e̶ ̶e̶n̶v̶i̶r̶o̶n̶m̶e̶n̶t̶ ̶o̶f̶ ̶t̶h̶e̶ ̶t̶r̶a̶c̶k̶s̶ ̶a̶n̶d̶ ̶a̶l̶s̶o̶ ̶s̶o̶m̶e̶ ̶b̶u̶g̶s̶ (Fixed);
As I said the steering is great for beginners , but it's annoying if you want to step up"

